Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

snippet.title: Girls Hostel - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Minku hai bahut bada khiladi (played by Amit Bhadana) jo ek sath 3-3 girlfriends ko ghuma raha hai aur unke gifts aur paise kha raha hai. Lekin ek din Minku ki life mein aa jata hai bhuchal jab ek girlfriend uske samne rakh deti hai ek demand. Ye sabhi ladkiyan rehti hai ek hi Girls Hostel mein. Kaise bachayega Minku apni jaan? Ye jaan jaoge aap agar dekhoge ye mazedar video.

snippet.title: Thozha - Back to Back comedy scene 2 | Karthi | Nagarjuna | Vivek | Tammanah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
The story revolves around Vikramadhitya (Nagarjuna) a quadriplegic billionaire, and Seenu, (Karthi) his ex-convict caretaker. Circumstances in their life teach them the value of relationships over money. 

Thozha is a 2016 movie . It was released in both Telugu and Tamil languages. Its name in Telugu is Oppri . The film is a remake of the French film The Intouchables . The film stars Karthik Sivakumar , Nagarsuna , Tamannaah , Prakasu Rasu , Vivek , Anushka , Seyashuda , Sireyya . The film is directed by Vamsi Baidipalli and produced by Prasad V Potluri.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Making Halloween Costume Vlog in Tamil | Sheep Costume for Kids
snippet.description:
In this video join as I make some Halloween costumes for Alandra and Alaric. This year, I decided to get creative and make matching sheep costumes, perfect for a fun family Halloween look. Simple, affordable materials, like cotton balls and a basic dress, can be easily transform them into cute, fluffy sheep outfits.
#halloweencostume #sheepcostume #steffivlogs

Gluing cotton balls onto the dress to give it that perfect wooly sheep appearance. These homemade costumes are not only budget-friendly but also a great DIY Halloween costume idea for parents who love crafting unique and personalized outfits for their children. I hope this week's vlog inspires you to make your own homemade sheep costumes and enjoy a fun-filled crafting session with your little ones! See you soon with more interesting videos.

snippet.title: 2 Minecraft Speedrunners VS TITAN
snippet.description:
2 Minecraft Speedrunners VS TITAN. You asked for it. The return of Minecraft Manhunt, George & Dream VS a real life Titan

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dream
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dreampublic

George: @GeorgeNotFound 

Merch: https://www.dream.shop

All video music is custom scored and produced by Dream & PmBata. 

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt 2: TITAN TAKEDOWN. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is a massive, near invincible TITAN, being controlled by a real life human projected into the game using our custom fusion technology, instead of multiple hunters. This is the toughest challenge I have faced yet. GeorgeNotFound and I are on a team of 2, and are trying to speedrun and beat the game.

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.21 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my anonymous friend tries everything he can to stop me. This is all custom coded by us. 

If this video somehow gets 1,000,000 likes we'll announce the date of the next episode early.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftManhunt #MinecraftManhunt2

-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Par Tane Manana Okha Se Jama Okha Se

Na Roj Ghumave Baat Re Bata Hakikat Ke Se
Aa Baith Ke Clear Karle Ne Tere Dikkat Ke Se
Kade Maane Kade Naraj Hove Is Baat Ka Na Koe Ilaj Hove
Roj Kehve Ib Nahi Ladu Tere Tisre Din Ke Khaaj Hove
Mera Ji Jaane Tu Kisa Hai Kd Nature Ka 
Aur Log Kehve Ke Chhora To Jama Koka Se
Haye Jod Ke Donu Hath Yo Rusya Ram Manalu Main
Par Tane Manana Okha Se Jama Okha Se

Tu To Mane Rani Kehya Karta Re
Mere Pe Kahani Kehya Karta Re
Ib Jama Pagla Ju Dikhu Tane
Pehla Jama Shyani Kehya Karda Re
Tu To Mane Cute Si Batave Tha
Bairi Kyate Jhuth Si Batave Tha
Ib Jama Jeher Jisi Laagu Tane
Re Pehla To Fruit Si Batave Tha
Acha Koni Lagda Re Bolna Yo Rude Tera
Yaad Hai Ke Pahle Kde Eisa Na Tha Mood Tera 
Kon Si Ne Krya Hai Yo Change Attitude Tera 
Side Muh Na Baat Kre Banga Rave Hood Tera

#gopalbhar #‡¶ó‡ßã‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶Å‡¶°‡¶º #funtimewithgopal 

About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

How to make perfect Besan Ladu Recipe | Halwai Style 1 kilo besan ladu recipe¬†

How to make Besan Laddu Flour -
 ‚Ä¢ Dry roast chana dal on very flame until they get light marks on it
 ‚Ä¢ Once done, allow the dal to comes at room temp & then take it to the flour mill for grinding
 ‚Ä¢ Make little coarse texture flour, which is perfect for laddus

How to make Besan laddu -
 ‚Ä¢ heat up some ghee into a kadhai, add besan & roast on low flame for 2-3 mins
 ‚Ä¢ then add some more besan & roast for 2 more mins, again add remaining besan & roast the besan on low flame until besan changes the color to light golden brown & get aromatic
 ‚Ä¢ While roasting the besan make sure to keep the flame low, roast continuously & break all the lumps from the besan
 ‚Ä¢ After 25 mins of roasting, if you find the besan is still dry then add some extra ghee
 ‚Ä¢ Once besan is roasted completely, sprinkle some water or milk & mix well for 2 mins & turn off the flame
 ‚Ä¢ Take the roasted besan to a parat or large plate & allow it to cool down
 ‚Ä¢ Once the roasted besan comes at room temp, add powder sugar & cardamom pw to it¬†
 ‚Ä¢ mix everything well, break sugar lumps if any & roll the laddus
 ‚Ä¢ Our delicious besan laddu is ready

How to make perfect Besan Ladu Recipe | Halwai Style 1 kilo besan ladu recipe¬†

How to make Besan Laddu Flour -
 ‚Ä¢ Dry roast chana dal on very flame until they get light marks on it
 ‚Ä¢ Once done, allow the dal to comes at room temp & then take it to the flour mill for grinding
 ‚Ä¢ Make little coarse texture flour, which is perfect for laddus

How to make Besan laddu -
 ‚Ä¢ heat up some ghee into a kadhai, add besan & roast on low flame for 2-3 mins
 ‚Ä¢ then add some more besan & roast for 2 more mins, again add remaining besan & roast the besan on low flame until besan changes the color to light golden brown & get aromatic
 ‚Ä¢ While roasting the besan make sure to keep the flame low, roast continuously & break all the lumps from the besan
 ‚Ä¢ After 25 mins of roasting, if you find the besan is still dry then add some extra ghee
 ‚Ä¢ Once besan is roasted completely, sprinkle some water or milk & mix well for 2 mins & turn off the flame
 ‚Ä¢ Take the roasted besan to a parat or large plate & allow it to cool down
 ‚Ä¢ Once the roasted besan comes at room temp, add powder sugar & cardamom pw to it¬†
 ‚Ä¢ mix everything well, break sugar lumps if any & roll the laddus
 ‚Ä¢ Our delicious besan laddu is ready

Lyrics-
Labhde firde maame tere pakke tikaane ve,
Laggu 26 ja 307 eh rabb hi jane ve,
Ho leke jamanat hafte vich aau bahar rakane ni,
Ho uthde behnde leader‚Äôan naal mere yaar rakane ni,
Ve laa laa naake sane gaddi tainu chakkan nu firde,
Ho darr na jattiye sade layi koi vadda masla nahi,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Jadd vi turde kafla naal tu leke turde ve,
Sheh ki jatt pendi na dasan di kade lod billo,
Dil dul ta ve lagda tera tutt da hona ni,
Kade kade vajjdiye pinde nu bas tod billo,
Taur Tappe to bina hor das ki ki kadh da o,
Kade kadai kande kade kadai tasla‚Äôan ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Darda vakil ve aulakha tera case koi fadd da nahi,
Saddi aakh kadhdiye kalli jane kaam koi khad da nahi,
Oh jadd tak ghar ni mud da ve dil jeha dar da rehnda ae,
Tere te hi marda aaukha saukha marda nahi,
Triple 0 1 LC vich kon ya hunda ve,
Jay virk jahe pakke yaar te nale pakkiya rafla ni,
Ve Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Tainu firde chakkan nu pale par tu thalle ni lagda,
Tahi ta tere aale jatt de utte lagde ni,
Ve dino dini tera tam jham jeha vadh da janda ae,
Mehar babe di sir te balliye tahio dabde nahi,
Vairi sadde ne naale tere te aakh ji rakde ne,
Hundiya ni tavi karde ne tere jatt diya nakla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,
Ik number da maal te do number da asla ni,
Teri talashi vicho police nu ki mil sakda ve,

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.
